This program analyses Photos, Videos, and Audio files using AI models for content description of Images, and transcripts for Audio contained.
It also calculates addresses of the photo and video locations.

The AI models used are all free of charge and offline downloaded on your computer.
No personal data is sent to some AI provider. 

For using the GPU power of your graphic card for the AI models, you may need to install torch, see below.
The models are also usable on a standard CPU. Time for image/frame analysis is 1-2 sec on a Surface Pro 8.
Time for audio transcripts of videos is approx. 1.5x the duration. Long videos may not work.


pip uninstall torch torchvision torchaudio -y
pip install torch torchvision torchaudio --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cu121   
# maybe cu118 or cu123 works better on your PC. Torch may only work for NVIDIA graphic cards.

